Sentencas: Pd promoted SM0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSC)-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15CO0.05O3-delta (LSGMC5) composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (ITSOFC) were prepared using the wet impregnation method.
Titulo: High performance Pd promoted Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3-δ composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: XRD analyses demonstrated that the Pd in the electrode was in the form of PdO.
Titulo: High performance Pd promoted Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3-δ composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The activity for oxygen reduction of the electrode increased with the increase in the concentration of Pd in the electrode and with the decrease in the electrode sintering temperature.
Titulo: High performance Pd promoted Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3-δ composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Pd sinteredat 1123 K showed an electrode resistance about 0.12 ohm cm(2) at near equilibrium conditions in oxygen at 873 K, which was only about one fourth of the electrode resistance without Pd addition.
Titulo: High performance Pd promoted Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3-δ composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The addition of Pd species in the electrode showed no obvious effect on the mechanism of the oxygen reduction reaction.
Titulo: High performance Pd promoted Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.15Co0.05O3-δ composite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
